search as well as the search term.

00:33:13.980 --> 00:33:15.920
and of course you can
run an Apple script.

00:33:16.130 --> 00:33:17.190
Here's the syntax for that.

00:33:17.300 --> 00:33:20.910
It's a help:run script and you give
the path to the Apple script that's

00:33:20.920 --> 00:33:22.900
included with your help content.

00:33:22.900 --> 00:33:26.080
You can also pass a parameter
to that Apple script.

00:33:26.090 --> 00:33:29.180
So you can generalize your
scripts and pass parameters to

00:33:29.250 --> 00:33:31.170
have them do specific things.

